title: GTA+
headline: GTA+
subtitle: The Vinewood Club Garage
content:
The Vinewood Club Garage is an extensive expansion to meet the vehicular storage needs of The Vinewood Club's clientele. On top of all your garage space in existing properties, GTA+ Members now have access to the full storage capacity of this new location in Pillbox Hill, right in the core of downtown Los Santos.

GTA+ Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel any time. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
